Infrastructure Design:

Server 1 (Primary Server):

Web Server (Nginx)
Application Server
Application Files (Your Code Base)
Database (MySQL - Primary)
Server 2 (Replica Server):

Application Server
Database (MySQL - Replica)
Load Balancer (HAproxy):

Distributes traffic between Server 1 and Server 2
